Reasoning: The paper focuses on the technical challenges of automated driving in urban environments, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) for perception and planning. The use of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is also mentioned. The demonstration of the AD system on a modified vehicle suggests a focus on machine learning and deep learning algorithms (cs.LG). Finally, the overall system architecture and the need for further investigation for full-scale roll-out suggest a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
